input_text.Prompt: Can you tell me how to use picture in picture?
input_text.Response A:
Make sure your TV has it!
Find the source(s)!
Engage the PIP by pressing the "PIP" button; a small box should appear in one corner of the screen.
input_text.Response B:
Do a search to see if your product already has an ASIN.
Go to your Amazon Seller Central page and then select Inventory >> Add a Product.
Type in whatever information that you have.
Rejoice if the search yields a product.
Click on See all product details.
Obtain some UPC codes for your product.

label_annotations.feedback: Response A was concise and clear and answered the question. Response B answered a different question altogether and was not useful at all.
